         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en"><p> Emperor Vespasian . . . ]ordered [the making of roads by the agency of] L(ucius) Minicius Rufus, proconsul. Mile 4. </p></div>
