         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>For the date and the formulae see <ref type="inscription" n="M.199">M.199</ref>, under the same proconsul, Lucius Minicius Rufus <title>PIR<hi rend="superscript">2</hi></title>, M 626;
               for a Minicius Rufus with, apparently, the praenomen of Aulus see on <ref type="inscription" n="C.273">C.273</ref>.</p>
